quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  73,20,tumhara perwar-digaar khoob jaanta hai ke tum aur tumahray sath ke log ( kabhi ) do tahai raat ke qareeb aur ( kabhi ) aadhi raat aur ( kabhi ) tahai raat qiyamkiya karte ho. aur khuda to raat aur din ka andaza rakhta hai. is ne maloomkiya ke tum is ko nibaah nah sakuu ge to is ne tum par meharbani ki. pas jitna aasani se hosakay ( itna ) quran parh liya karo. is ne jana ke tum mein baaz bemaar bhi hotay hain aur baaz khuda ke fazl ( yani muaash ) ki talaash mein malik mein safar karte hain aur baaz khuda ki raah mein lartay hain. to jitna aasani se hosakay itna parh liya karo. aur namaz parhte raho aur zakaat ada karte raho aur khuda ko naik ( aur khuloos niyat se ) qarz dete raho. aur jo amal naik tum apne liye agay bhaijho ge is ko khuda ke haan behtar aur siilay mein buzurag tar pao ge. aur khuda se bakhshish mangte raho. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  74,1,ae ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) jo kapra lapete parre ho
  74,2,utho aur hadaayat karo
  74,3,aur apne perwar-digaar ki barayi karo
  74,4,aur apne kapron ko pak rakho
  74,5,aur napaaki se daur raho
  74,6,aur ( is niyat se ) ahsaan nah karo ke is se ziyada ke taalib ho
  74,7,aur apne perwar-digaar ke liye sabr karo
  74,8,jab sor phonka jaye ga
  74,9,woh din ka mushkil din hoga
  74,10,( yani ) kafiroon par aasaan nah hoga
  74,11,hamein is shakhs se samajh lainay do jis ko hum ne akela pedakiya
  74,12,aur maal kaseer diya
  74,13,aur ( har waqt is ke paas ) haazir rehne walay betay diye
  74,14,aur har terhan ke samaan mein wusat di
  74,15,abhi khwahish rakhta hai ke aur ziyada den
  74,16,aisa hargiz nahi hoga. yeh hamari ayatain ka dushman raha hai
  74,17,hum usay Saood par charhayen ge
